<lb n="0926b05"/><head type="no">No. 1411</head><div1 type="dharani">
<lb n="0926b06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0926001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說蓮華眼陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0926b07"/>
<lb n="0926b08"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0926002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（西天…臣））二十字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0926002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣）二十字＝（三藏法師）四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0926002"><lem>西天<note n="0926003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0926003"><lem>譯經</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿
<lb n="0926b09"/>傳法大師<note n="0926004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0926004"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣</rdg></app>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0926b10"/><p type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野曩麼阿<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0926b11"/>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;納摩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">引</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>野怛他<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0926b12"/>&CB00344;<note n="0926005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哆＝多【三】</note><note n="0926005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哆＝多【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0926005"><lem>哆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">多</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>野曩謨薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;&CB00085;囉拏尾瑟迦
<lb n="0926b13"/><note place="inline">二合</note>鼻尼&CB00155;地薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>野摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>薩怛&CB00085;
<lb n="0926b14"/><note place="inline">二合</note>野怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>哆囉哆囉底哩底
<lb n="0926b15"/>哩&CB00418;嚕&CB00418;嚕迦羅迦羅吉&CB00619;吉&CB00619;俱嚕俱嚕婆
<lb n="0926b16"/>囉婆囉鼻哩鼻哩部嚕部嚕曩野曩野俱嚕俱
<lb n="0926b17"/>嚕謨乞叉<note place="inline">二合引</note>播野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅
<lb n="0926b18"/>曩&CB00085;呬&CB00135;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;鼻<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0926b19"/>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;哆<note place="inline">引</note>底瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀麼
<lb n="0926b20"/>麼薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>難左娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0926b21"/><p>此蓮華眼陀羅尼。若復有人於其晨朝恭敬
<lb n="0926b22"/>供養。及念此陀羅尼一百八遍。一日二日乃
<lb n="0926b23"/>至<note n="0926006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＋（十）【三】</note><note n="0926006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＋（十）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0926006"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三十</rdg></app>七日<note n="0926007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝至【元】【明】</note><app n="0926007"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>心持誦。一切罪障悉皆除滅。
<lb n="0926b24"/>亦不患其眼病耳病鼻舌身病。心不邪亂。復
<lb n="0926b25"/>得五種眼清淨五種<note n="0926008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鼻＝病【明】</note><app n="0926008"><lem>鼻</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">病</rdg></app>清淨。五種舌清淨五
<lb n="0926b26"/>種意清淨。身相端直心離垢染。於一切生中
<lb n="0926b27"/>&M010527;發菩提心。與諸聖眾常得見佛。而聽妙法
<lb n="0926b28"/>直至菩提道場圓滿正覺</p>
<lb n="0926b29"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說蓮華眼陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
